    "content": "\n# [Luthor](/demo/) Documentation Index\r\n\r\nThis is the canonical documentation root for the monorepo.\r\n\r\n## User Documentation\r\n\r\n- Demo getting started: [user/demo/getting-started.md](/docs/reference/user/demo/getting-started/)\r\n- Demo usage and persistence: [user/demo/usage-and-persistence.md](/docs/reference/user/demo/usage-and-persistence/)\r\n- [Luthor](/demo/) getting started: [user/luthor/getting-started.md](/docs/reference/user/luthor/getting-started/)\r\n- [Luthor](/demo/) presets and configuration: [user/luthor/presets-and-configuration.md](/docs/reference/user/luthor/presets-and-configuration/)\r\n- Extensive editor guide: [user/luthor/extensive-editor.md](/docs/reference/user/luthor/extensive-editor/)\r\n- Headless getting started: [user/headless/getting-started.md](/docs/reference/user/headless/getting-started/)\r\n- Headless extensions and configuration: [user/headless/extensions-and-configuration.md](/docs/reference/user/headless/extensions-and-configuration/)\r\n- Headless import/export: [user/headless/import-export.md](/docs/reference/user/headless/import-export/)\r\n- Tutorial: [user/demo/usage-and-persistence.md](/docs/reference/user/demo/usage-and-persistence/)\r\n\r\n## Developer Documentation\r\n\r\n- Demo architecture: [developer/demo/architecture.md](/docs/reference/developer/demo/architecture/)\r\n- Demo source file reference: [developer/demo/source-file-reference.md](/docs/reference/developer/demo/source-file-reference/)\r\n- Demo maintainer notes: [developer/demo/maintainer-notes.md](/docs/reference/developer/demo/maintainer-notes/)\r\n- [Luthor](/demo/) architecture: [developer/luthor/architecture.md](/docs/reference/developer/luthor/architecture/)\r\n- [Luthor](/demo/) file-by-file reference: [developer/luthor/source-file-reference.md](/docs/reference/developer/luthor/source-file-reference/)\r\n- [Luthor](/demo/) maintainer notes: [developer/luthor/maintainer-notes.md](/docs/reference/developer/luthor/maintainer-notes/)\r\n- Headless architecture: [developer/headless/architecture.md](/docs/reference/developer/headless/architecture/)\r\n- Headless file-by-file reference: [developer/headless/source-file-reference.md](/docs/reference/developer/headless/source-file-reference/)\r\n- Headless maintainer notes: [developer/headless/maintainer-notes.md](/docs/reference/developer/headless/maintainer-notes/)\r\n- README mapping: [developer_notes/readme-map.md](/docs/reference/developer_notes/readme-map/)\r\n\r\n## Package READMEs (mandatory)\r\n\r\n- Monorepo README: [../README.md](https://github.com/lyfie-app/luthor/blob/main/README.md)\r\n- Headless README: [../packages/headless/README.md](https://github.com/lyfie-app/luthor/blob/main/packages/headless/README.md)\r\n- [Luthor](/demo/) presets README: [../packages/luthor/README.md](https://github.com/lyfie-app/luthor/blob/main/packages/luthor/README.md)\r\n",
